title: 💕Spacious 1x1+Office just Steps from South Lamar!💕

posting_body: ['1 bedroom + office by South Lamar!', '*If you sign up with our preferred renters insurance provider, ePremium, we can waive $100 off the security deposit, as well as waive the $200 pet deposits if you have pets!', '🐾 Mention this ad!*', 'APARTMENT FEATURES', 'Pictures are of actual unit - available August✿', 'You will have 813 sqft and a covered private patio!', 'The unit is located on the first floor and is going for $1650/month.', 'There are Google Fiber jacks installed in each unit, but you still have the option to choose a different internet provider if you’d like.', 'Electricity is set up through the City of Austin.', 'Water is allocated and will show up on your monthly rent statement; it is about $25/person.', 'There is a 24/7 on-site laundry facility.', 'It is $1/wash and $1/dry!', 'COMMUNITY FEATURES', 'No breed restrictions/weight limits', 'Off leash dog park', 'Swimming pool', 'Property security', 'Near transportation + very walkable!', 'Laundry Facility on site', '24/7 maintenance', 'Guest parking', 'Off-street parking', 'Covered balcony', 'Popular area by South Lamar', 'Private and tucked away location!', 'Contact info:', 'Zoee', 'Tramor at Creek Village & Quest', 'show contact info', 'or Cell:', 'show contact info']
